title: League wont update
body:
So I just got an update not too long ago, my update goes to 33% then proceeds to give me this message: "unspecified error occurred. Please check the logs for more information." anyone know a fix?
Thanks.

replies.body: Are you still having this problem?  There was an issue with patching earlier, but everything is okay now.  Let me know, and I'd be happy to help!
